            <div type="translation">
                <p>I am the Lord’s servant. May your word to me be fulfilled.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Poor condition. Exfoliated. A cross with dots in the angles marks the beginning of the text. The inscription is based on the dialoque between the Archangel Gabriel and the Virgin according to Luke 1:28, 38.</p>
            </div>
